'''气旋古努'''（{{lang-en|Cyclone Gonu}}，[[印度气象局|印度气象局]]编号：'''{{lang|en|ARB}} 01'''，[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]编号：'''02{{lang|en|A}}'''）又名'''超级气旋风暴古努'''（{{lang|en|Super Cyclonic Storm Gonu}}），是[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]有纪录以来最强烈的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，而該記錄在2019年時被[[氣旋基亞爾|超級氣旋風暴基亞爾]]所打破。作为[[2007年北印度洋气旋季|2007年北印度洋气旋季]]第2场获得命名的风暴，古努源于这年6月1日阿拉伯海东部持续存在的[[对流|对流]]区。据印度气象局估算，系统因上层大气环境有利且[[海面温度|水温]]较高而[[快速增强|快速增强]]，于6月3日达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]240公里的最高强度。接下来风暴因行经洋面空气干燥且水温降低而逐渐减弱，于6月6日清晨从[[阿曼|阿曼]]最东端[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，刷新吹袭[[阿拉伯半岛|阿拉伯半岛]]热带气旋的强度纪录。风暴转向北上进入[[阿曼湾|阿曼湾]]，从[[伊朗|伊朗]]南部登陆，成为1898年后首场登陆该国的热带气旋，最终于6月7日消散。

阿拉伯海极少出现像古努这样强烈的热带气旋，该海域的绝大多数风暴通常规模都很小，并且很快就会消散<ref>{{cite web | url = http://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/NaturalHazards/view.php?id=18436 | title = NASA Earth Observatory: Tropical Cyclone Gonu | date = 2007-06-04 | accessdate = 2014-09-27 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-09-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140927024934/http://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/NaturalHazards/view.php?id=18436 | publisher = [[美国航空航天局|NASA]]}}</ref>。气旋在阿曼夺走50条人命，还造成价值42亿美元（2007年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|4200000000|2007}}}}美元）的巨额损失，成为该国历史上最惨烈的自然灾害。古努还在阿拉伯海东部海岸线附近产生大量降水，最高降雨量达610毫米，引发严重洪灾并造成重大破坏。伊朗也有28人丧生，损失数额约为2.16亿美元（2007年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|216000000|2007}}}}美元）。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Gonu 2007 track.png}}
2007年5月末，[[季风槽|季风槽]]在[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]东部催生出[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref name="imd">{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2008-01 |title=Report on Cyclonic Disturbances over North Indian Ocean during 2007 |accessdate=2008-11-26 |url=http://sonicfighters.com/rattleman/other/tropics/IMD_2007_Report_HTML.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ccClL6ET?url=http://sonicfighters.com/rattleman/other/tropics/IMD_2007_Report_HTML.html |archivedate=2008-11-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。到5月31日时，印度[[孟买|孟买]]以南约645公里海域已形成组织结构良好的[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]，还带有气旋式[[对流|对流]]（即[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动）和层次分明的中层环流。这股扰动天气起初缺乏明显的下层环流，而是在地面[[低压槽|低压槽]]西部边缘附近拥有强烈的[[辐散|辐散]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Delta Forecast Team |date=2007-05-31 |title=May 31 Significant Tropical Weather Advisory for the North Indian Ocean |publisher=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PKajUuuL?url=http://sonicfighters.com/rattleman/042534-abioweb.txt |url=http://sonicfighters.com/rattleman/042534-abioweb.txt |deadurl=yes |format=TXT |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archivedate=2007-06-03 }}</ref>。由于上层大气环境有利，对流得以改善<ref>{{cite web |author=Charlie Forecast Team |date=2007-06-01 |title=June 1 Significant Tropical Weather Advisory for the North Indian Ocean |publisher=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PKajUuuL?url=http://sonicfighters.com/rattleman/042534-abioweb.txt |archivedate=2007-06-03 |deadurl=yes |format=TXT |url=http://sonicfighters.com/rattleman/042534-abioweb.txt }}</ref>，到6月1日晚，系统已有足够发展，印度气象局因此将其归类为低气压<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-02 |title=June 2 Tropical Weather Outlook |accessdate=2007-06-03 |url=http://www.sonicfighters.com/rattleman/203330-rsmc.htm |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PKZlyZuA?url=http://www.sonicfighters.com/rattleman/203330-rsmc.htm |archivedate=2007-06-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。低气压在印度南部上空沿中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]的西南边缘向西移动，其对流继续组织，[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]于6月2日清晨将位于孟买西南方向约685公里洋面的系统归类为第02{{lang|en|A}}号热带气旋<ref name="warn1">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-02 |title=Tropical Cyclone 02A Warning NR 001 |accessdate=2007-06-02 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PI4P6577?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archivedate=2007-06-02 |deadurl=yes |format=TXT }}</ref>。

低气压刚形成时，其西北方向受到干燥空气的侵蚀，气象机构预计这会令其增强程度受限<ref name="warn1" />。气旋稳步强化，印度气象局于6月2日将其升级成[[热带气旋风级|深低气压]]<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-02 |title=Deep Depression over East Central Arabian Sea |accessdate=2007-06-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PI3E1mSw?url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2007-06-02 }}</ref>，再于当天晚上将位于印度孟买西南方向约760公里海域的系统归类为气旋风暴并以“古努”（{{lang|en|Gona}}）命名<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-02 |title=Cyclone Storm "GONU" over East Central Arabian Sea |accessdate=2007-06-02 |archivedate=2007-06-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PIRtXOfN?url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。由于[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]上空有中[[纬度|纬度]]低压槽发展形成，气旋转朝北面及东北方向前进<ref name="warn4">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-02 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 004 |accessdate=2007-06-03 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PJM7tPiw?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archivedate=2007-06-03 |format=TXT |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但在北面有高压脊逐渐形成后又回转向西移动<ref name="warn5">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-03 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 005 |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PJgtZuxr?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archivedate=2007-06-03 |deadurl=yes |format=TXT }}</ref>。风暴内拥有密实的强烈对流区，并且[[快速增强|快速增强]]，于6月3日清晨达到强烈气旋标准<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-03 |title=Severe Cyclone Storm "GONU" over East Central Arabian Sea |accessdate=2007-06-03 |url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |archivedate=2007-06-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PJM7lt7l?url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm }}</ref>；联合台风警报中心也认为，气旋拥有良好[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]，强度已达到飓风的最低标准<ref name="warn6">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |format=TXT |date=2007-06-03 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 006 |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archivedate=2007-06-03 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PK57ccI9?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。干燥空气最终对古努增强过程产生的影响小于之前预期，对流中心发展出层次分明的[[风眼|风眼]]，气旋在行经水温升高的局部洋面后快速强化<ref name="warn7">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-03 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 007 |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PKZ3UgwO?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archivedate=2007-06-03 |format=TXT |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

[[File:TC_Gonu_05_June_07_0635Z.jpg|thumb]]

6月3日晚，印度气象局将风暴升级成特强气旋风暴古努<ref name="63strongest">{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-03 |title=Very Severe Cyclonic Storm "GONU" over East Central Arabian Sea |accessdate=2007-06-03 |url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |archivedate=2007-06-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PKb1SriX?url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm }}</ref>。受水温较高<ref name="rsmc">{{cite report | title = A Report on the Super Cyclonic Storm “GONU” during 1-7 June, 2007 | author = Ajit Tyagi | publisher = India Meteorological Department | date = 2011-02 | accessdate = 2016-02-14 | url = http://www.rsmcnewdelhi.imd.gov.in/images/pdf/publications/met-monograph/gonu/gonu.pdf | format = PDF | display-authors = etal | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141014160510/http://www.rsmcnewdelhi.imd.gov.in/images/pdf/publications/met-monograph/gonu/gonu.pdf | archivedate = 2014-10-14}}</ref>、垂直[[风切变|风切变]]很少，以及上层大气外流环境良好的三重利好因素影响，古努进一步增强，在阿曼近海[[马西拉岛|马西拉岛]]的[[罗盘方位|东南偏东]]方向约285公里洋面达到[[最大持续风速|1分钟持续风速]]每小时270公里的最高强度<ref name="jtwcbt" />，并且这时其阵风时速已达315公里<ref name="warn10">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-04 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 010 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2007-06-04 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archivedate=2007-06-04 |format=TXT |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PLcPHPzA?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt }}</ref>。6月4日晚，印度气象局把系统升级成超级气旋风暴，其3分钟持续风速达每小时240公里，估计[[气压|气压]]值920[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]）<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-04 |title=A Super Cyclonic Storm "GONU" over East Central and adjoining westcentral and north Arabian Sea |accessdate=2007-06-04 |archivedate=2007-06-04 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PLm4Iqk8?url=http://www.imd.ernet.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm }}</ref>。古努至此成为有纪录以来阿拉伯海形成的第一场超级气旋风暴<ref name="rsmc" />。

风暴在最高强度下保持了约6小时，印度气象局于6月4日晚将古努降级成特强气旋风暴<ref name="imd" />。气旋的风眼内开始有云层遮盖并变得模糊，并因逼近[[阿拉伯半岛|阿拉伯半岛]]期间行经海域水温渐低、空气变得干燥而逐渐减弱<ref name="warn12">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-05 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 012 |accessdate=2007-06-05 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PMOutn5z?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archivedate=2007-06-05 |deadurl=yes |format=TXT }}</ref>。古努同阿曼陆地相互影响，其深层对流的内层核心迅速消亡，风力时速经过24小时后已下降95公里<ref name="disc15">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-05 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 015 |accessdate=2007-06-05 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archivedate=2007-06-05 |format=TXT |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PNXV1Qvn?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt }}</ref>。据印度气象局记载，气旋于6月6日清晨从阿曼最东端经过，并且这时仍有特强气旋风暴强度<ref name="imd" />。古努的风速还在逐渐减缓，但整体结构却在登陆数小时前略有改善，风眼虽然模糊，但下层结构依然层次分明<ref name="warn16">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-06 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 016 |accessdate=2007-06-06 |deadurl=yes |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PNsshR8D?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |format=TXT |archivedate=2007-06-06 }}</ref>。

进入[[阿曼湾|阿曼湾]]后，古努呈现出短暂的增强趋势<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |deadurl=yes |date=2007-06-06 |url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |title=Very Severe Cyclonic Storm "GONU". |accessdate=2007-06-06 |archivedate=2007-06-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5POG671lJ?url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm }}</ref>，这一趋势有可能是因水温较高引起<ref name="rsmc" />。但由于风切变增多，还有来自阿拉伯半岛的干燥空气侵入，风暴东部半圆内的深层对流被不断剥离<ref name="warn17">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-06 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 017 |accessdate=2007-06-06 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5POX3dA7y?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |format=TXT |archivedate=2007-06-06 }}</ref>。6月6日当天，古努转向西北偏北<ref name="warn18">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |date=2007-06-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5POfdmTti?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 018 |accessdate=2007-06-06 |format=TXT |archivedate=2007-06-06 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，联合台风警报中心于当晚将气旋降级成热带风暴<ref name="warn19">{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |deadurl=yes |date=2007-06-06 |title=Tropical Cyclone Gonu Warning NR 019 |accessdate=2007-06-06 |archivedate=2007-06-06 |url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PP3A1qrk?url=https://metocph.nmci.navy.mil/jtwc/warnings/io0207web.txt |format=TXT }}</ref>，印度气象局则在次日清晨跟进，先把古努降级成强烈气旋风暴，之后又再度归类为气旋风暴<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-07 |title=Cyclonic Storm "GONU". |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2007-06-07 |url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |archivedate=2007-06-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PPRTSo6e?url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |deadurl=yes |date=2007-06-07 |title=Severe Cyclonic Storm "GONU". |accessdate=2007-06-07 |archivedate=2007-06-07 |url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PPFzf3AI?url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |format=TXT }}</ref>。6小时后，古努已经穿越伊朗[[莫克兰|莫克兰]]海岸，印度气象局随即停止针对这场风暴发布公告<ref>{{cite web |author=India Meteorological Department |date=2007-06-07 |title=Cyclonic Storm "GONU". |accessdate=2007-06-07 |url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5PPjR9ouo?url=http://www.imd.gov.in/section/nhac/dynamic/rsmc.htm |deadurl=yes |format=TXT |archivedate=2007-06-07 }}</ref>。古努也至此成为1898年后首场吹袭伊朗的热带气旋。登陆后，气旋的残留低气压在伊朗上空持续到6月8日<ref name="rsmc" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
阿曼全国民防委员会主席马利克·宾·苏莱曼·阿尔曼玛里（{{lang|en|Malek Bin Sulaiman Al Ma'amari}}）将军表示，该国已制订应急预案，其中包括在风暴过去后动用军队和警方人员。媒体报道预计气旋会造成重大破坏，并以东北部地区灾情严重，降雨量可能在150毫米以上并伴有狂风。<ref>{{cite news | author = Sunil K. Vaidya | date = 207-06-04 | title = Tropical cyclonic storm to strike eastern coast of Oman | accessdate = 2016-02-14 | work = Gulf News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151225110910/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/7-000-mobilised-to-handle-cyclone-1.113020 | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/7-000-mobilised-to-handle-cyclone-1.113020 | archivedate = 2015-12-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>政府官员建议可能受风暴影响地区的居民撤离<ref name="reut64">{{cite web | agency = [[路透社|Reuters]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090705032533/http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L04784687.htm | date = 2007-06-04 | title = Oman on alert for cyclone—official news agency | accessdate = 2009-07-05 | archivedate = 2009-07-05 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L04784687.htm}}</ref>，[[马西拉岛|马西拉岛]]有约7000人因狂风和巨浪的威胁被迫疏散<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 2007-06-04 | title = Oman evacuates eastern island as powerful storm approaches | accessdate = 2009-07-05 | archivedate = 2009-07-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090705033101/http://www.pr-inside.com/oman-evacuates-eastern-island-as-powerful-r143801.htm | url = http://www.pr-inside.com/oman-evacuates-eastern-island-as-powerful-r143801.htm | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。该国宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="reut64" />，一共有2万余人躲进应急避难所<ref name="ap66">{{cite news|author=Saeed Al-Nahdy |agency=Associated Press |date=2007-06-06 |title=Cyclone Hammers Oman; Veers Toward Iran |accessdate=2016-02-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160214160348/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/06/06/AR2007060600318_pf.html |via=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |archivedate=2016-02-14 |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/06/06/AR2007060600318_pf.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>。阿曼国家气象局发出警报，称气旋的破坏力很可能会比[[1977年阿曼气旋|1977年袭击马西拉岛的毁灭性气旋]]更强<ref>{{cite news | author = Agencies | date = 2007-06-05 | title = Cyclone reaches Omani coast | work = Gulf News | accessdate = 2016-02-14 | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/cyclone-reaches-omani-coast-1.182952 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151225110932/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/cyclone-reaches-omani-coast-1.182952 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-12-25}}</ref>。该国东北部的费赫勒港原油码头因风暴威胁关闭超过3天之久<ref name="reut67">{{cite news | author = Lin Noueihed | date = 2007-06-07 | title = Cyclone Gonu weakens to a storm on way to Iran | agency = Reuters Alertnet | accessdate = 2009-07-08 | url = http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L0768732.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090708142753/http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L0768732.htm | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2009-07-08}}</ref>。阿曼官方将多个政府机构关闭2天，并宣布全国休假5天，沿海地区的大部分商户和企业都在政府宣布休假前关闭<ref>{{cite news | author = Sunil Vaidya | date = 2007-06-05 | accessdate = 2016-02-14 | work = Gulf News | title = Oman declares Gonu public holiday | archivedate = 2015-12-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151225110941/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/oman-declares-gonu-public-holiday-1.183063 | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/oman-declares-gonu-public-holiday-1.183063}}</ref>。受气旋影响，[[马斯喀特国际机场|马斯喀特国际机场]]当局从[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月5日晚20点起取消所有航班<ref>{{cite news | author = Sunil Vaidya | date = 2007-06-05 | title = Oman cancels all flights | agency = ''Gulf News'' | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151225111014/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/oman-cancels-all-flights-1.183186 | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/oman-cancels-all-flights-1.183186 | archivedate = 2015-12-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

[[File:Gonu_rainfall.jpg|left]]

[[石油输出国组织|石油输出国组织]]成员[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]和[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿拉伯联合酋长国]]都没有针对古努发布官方警报，预计风暴也不会对这两个国家的原油供应构成不利影响<ref name="reut64" />。但由于担心气旋对炼油设施构成破坏，再加上非洲最大产油国[[尼日利亚|尼日利亚]]面临全国性罢工的威胁，油价还是在6月5日早上开始上涨。从[[纽约商品期货交易所|纽约商品期货交易所]]星期一的收盘数据来看，7月交货的原油价格每桶上涨1.13美元，涨幅1.7%，达到66.21美元，是15天来最高的收盘价格。油价还一度攀升到66.48美元，是4月30日后的盘中最高价位。油价接下来呈小幅回落，周二上午9点43分，[[新加坡|新加坡]]的盘后电子交易成交价格为每桶65.95美元，比前日收盘价低26美分。<ref>{{cite web|author=Aaron Sheldrick |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120721190251/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aPdz6pzKBeYs&refer=home |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601087&sid=aPdz6pzKBeYs&refer=home |title=Gonu Weakens to Category Four Storm, Heads for Oman |accessdate=2012-07-21 |date=2007-06-05 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-07-21 |publisher=Bloomberg }}</ref>不过，石油价格信息服务公司首席石油分析师汤姆·克罗扎（{{lang|en|Tom Kloza}}）表示，他觉得此次油价上升未必是古努造成。在他看来，这场风暴并非涨价的真正原因，而不过是一种借口。<ref>{{cite web |author=Al Jazeera |title=Oman on high alert as cyclone nears |date=2007-06-06 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-02-15 |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2007/06/2008525123637703163.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ozqzVeJS?url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/middleeast/2007/06/2008525123637703163.html |archivedate=2010-04-15 }}</ref>

巴基斯坦官员建议渔夫不要前往距离海岸线超过50公里海域，预计开放海域会有大浪<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Pakistan Daily Times | date = 2007-06-04 | title = Tropical cyclone heading to Sindh coast | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020113132/http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=2007%5C06%5C05%5Cstory_5-6-2007_pg12_4 | url = http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=2007%5C06%5C05%5Cstory_5-6-2007_pg12_4 | accessdate = 2012-10-20 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。美国海军还向阿拉伯海的船员发出警报，建议他们尽可能避开这场风暴<ref>{{cite web |author=DowJones News |date=2007-06-04 |title=Crude Rallies On Rising Demand, Gulf Storm, Russia |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2016-02-15 |archivedate=2010-04-15 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.marketwatch.com/story/crude-rallies-on-rising-demand-gulf-storm-russia?siteid=yhoof |work=MarketWatch |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5oztgiXDF?url=http://www.marketwatch.com/story/crude-rallies-on-rising-demand-gulf-storm-russia?siteid=yhoof }}</ref>。

伊朗气象局向该国东南沿海发布风暴警告，预计相应地区会有中到重度降水并伴随强烈阵风<ref name="ap65" />。伊朗沿海地区有约4万人在气旋抵达前向内陆后撤至少1公里<ref name="afp67">{{cite web | author = Agence France-Presse | date = 2007-06-06 | title = Iran evacuates thousands as cyclone strikes | accessdate = 2009-07-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090705001540/http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200706/s1944500.htm | archivedate = 2009-07-05 | url = http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200706/s1944500.htm}}</ref>，其中包括[[恰赫巴哈尔国际大学|恰赫巴哈尔国际大学]]的约4000名学子<ref name="irna67">{{cite web | author = Islamic Republic News Agency | date = 2007-06-06 | title = Gonu Cyclone keeps lashing southern Iranian islands, cities | url = http://www.payvand.com/news/07/jun/1061.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120511062903/http://www.payvand.com/news/07/jun/1061.html | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-05-11}}</ref>。进出科纳拉克机场的所有航班停飞48小时，[[锡斯坦－俾路支斯坦省|锡斯坦－俾路支斯坦省]]的所有医院均进入红色警戒状态<ref name="irna67" />。[[国际红十字与红新月运动|国际红十字会]]伊朗分会提前运送必要的救灾物资<ref name="irfc611">{{cite web|author=International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies |date=2007-06-11 |title=Iran: Cyclone Gonu Information Bulletin No. 2 |publisher=Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs |url=http://reliefweb.int/report/iran-islamic-republic/iran-cyclone-gonu-information-bulletin-no-2 |accessdate=2016-02-15 |archivedate=2012-12-12 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121212233510/http://reliefweb.int/report/iran-islamic-republic/iran-cyclone-gonu-information-bulletin-no-2 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Gonu_Damage_in_Qurum_Beach_1.JPG|thumb]]受到破坏的道路]]
气旋古努沿途造成大量人员伤亡和严重破坏<ref name="imd" />。早在从阿曼东海岸线附近掠过之前7小时，风暴就开始在该国产生狂风暴雨，沿海地区降雨量高达610毫米<ref name="gn60507" /><ref name="dn611">{{cite web|deadurl=no |date=2007-06-11 |title=Gonu inflicts $1bn damage |accessdate=2016-02-15 |publisher=Daily News |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215142726/http://archives.gdnonline.com/NewsDetails.aspx?date=04%2F07%2F2015&storyid=185051 |url=http://archives.gdnonline.com/NewsDetails.aspx?date=04/07/2015&storyid=185051 |archivedate=2016-02-15 }}</ref>。气旋令阿曼大部分海岸线受到大浪冲击<ref name="gn60507">{{cite web | author = Sunil Vaidya, Bureau Chief, Oman and Daniel Bardsley, Staff Reporter, and Aftab Kazmi | date = 2007-06-05 | title = Gulf States on Gonu alert | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/gulf-states-on-gonu-alert-1.106059 | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151225110955/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/gulf-states-on-gonu-alert-1.106059 | work = Gulf News | archivedate = 2015-12-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，许多沿海道路被淹<ref name="ap65">{{cite news |author=Saeed Al-Nahdy |date=2007-06-05 |title=Cyclone Gonu's Winds Blast Oman Coast |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2016-02-15 |url=http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Cyclone-Gonus-winds-blast-Oman-coast |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ozuq23uf?url=http://www.jpost.com/MiddleEast/Article.aspx?id=63860 |archivedate=2010-04-15 }}</ref>。腊斯哈德的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]高达5.1米，海水侵入内陆约200米远，其它沿海地区也有类似情况<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/j.ecss.2009.10.019 | last1 = Fritz | first1 = Hermann M. | last2 = Fritz | first2 = HM | last3 = Blount | first3 = CD | last4 = Albusaidi | first4 = FB | year = 2010 | title = Cyclone Gonu storm surge in Oman | journal = Estuarine Coastal and Shelf Science | volume = 86 | issue = 1 | pages = 102–106 | bibcode = 2010ECSS...86..102F | display-authors = etal}}</ref>。

=== 阿曼 ===
阿曼东部各地的供电和电话线路因狂风中断，数千人同外界失去联系，直至数小时后线路恢复。风暴在该国海岸沿线引起大范围破坏，受灾地区包括阿曼陆地最东端的[[苏尔_(阿曼)|苏尔]]和腊斯哈德。<ref name="gn66">{{cite web | author = Sunil Vaidya | date = 2007-06-06 | title = Muscat lashed by Cyclone Gonu | work = Gulf News | accessdate = 2007-06-09 | url = http://www.gulfnews.com/region/Oman/10130416.html | archivedate = 2007-06-09 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070609133209/http://www.gulfnews.com/region/Oman/10130416.html}}</ref>首都[[马斯喀特|马斯喀特]]的风速达到每小时100公里，导致该市停电。强烈的海浪和暴雨将多条街道和部分建筑物淹没，该市警务人员通过发送手机短信提醒居民远离被淹的街道，防止触电。据报道，该国油田所受破坏程度很轻。<ref name="ap66" />年产约1000万吨[[液化天然气|液化天然气]]的苏尔受气旋重创，无法继续开采<ref name="Reuters-DialaSaadeh">{{cite web | author = Diala Saadeh | date = 2007-06-08 | title = Cyclone Gonu leaves Oman, heads towards Iran | publisher = Reuters | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090705032546/http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L08269325.htm | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2009-07-05 | url = http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L08269325.htm | archivedate = 2009-07-05 | via = AlertNet}}</ref>。整场风暴一共在阿曼夺走50条人命，气旋过去4天后，该国尚有27人失踪<ref name="imd" />。全国约有2万人受灾<ref>{{cite web | author = Indo-Asian News Service | date = 2007-06-10 | title = Cyclone Gonu kills 12 in Iran, Gulf toll 61 | accessdate = 2008-05-10 | url = http://www.mangalorean.com/news.php?newstype=local&newsid=45412 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080510224420/http://mangalorean.com/news.php?newstype=local&newsid=45412 | archivedate = 2008-05-10 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，经济损失估计达42亿美元（2007年美元）<ref name="imd" />。

=== 阿拉伯联合酋长国 ===
古努产生的猛烈海浪将大量海水推向阿拉伯联合酋长国[[富吉拉|富吉拉]]的沿海地区，多条道路被迫封闭，车流只能改道。民防机构和警务部门值班监控封闭的道路，市政工人则将积水抽离路面。连接卡尔巴和富吉拉的道路也因水淹封闭。<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-06-05 | title = Fujairah hit by Cyclone Gonu | work = Gulf News | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/uae/environment/storm-hits-fujairah-1.183064 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908212636/http://gulfnews.com/news/uae/environment/storm-hits-fujairah-1.183064 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-09-08}}</ref>据报道，海岸沿线出现高达10米的狂浪，十余艘渔船因此被毁，另有约300艘船被水带走，或是其中的物品被水冲走<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-06-08 | title = Gonu sends fish prices soaring | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/uae/environment/gonu-sends-fish-prices-soaring-1.183207 | work = Gulf News | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102201138/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/uae/environment/gonu-sends-fish-prices-soaring-1.183207}}</ref>，富吉拉港总体受创严重。港口内还有一艘船沉没，船上10人失踪<ref>{{cite web | author = United Press International | date = 2007-06-10 | title = Iran surveys damage after cyclone | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102200603/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/2007/06/09/Iran-surveys-damage-after-cyclone/UPI-75861181409342/ | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.upi.com/Top_News/2007/06/09/Iran-surveys-damage-after-cyclone/UPI-75861181409342/}}</ref>。

=== 伊朗和巴基斯坦 ===
吹袭伊朗期间，气旋降下中到暴雨，[[恰赫巴哈尔|恰赫巴哈尔]]的降雨量为74毫米<ref name="afp67" />，风速达到每小时111公里<ref name="ap66" />，引起停电，并导致部分土坯民宅受损<ref name="afp67" />，停电还在城内多地引发火灾。降雨致使至少40幢房屋被淹<ref name="irna67" />，还令多条主要道路临时封闭<ref name="ap66" />。风暴在部分地区产生2米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="reut610">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Reuters | date = 2007-06-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100330153245/http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L10319787.htm | title = Death toll in Iran from cyclone climbs to 23 | url = http://www.alertnet.org/thenews/newsdesk/L10319787.htm | accessdate = 2010-03-30 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2010-03-30}}</ref>，许多建在沿海地区的民房因此受损<ref name="reut67" />。[[贾斯克|贾斯克]]的1条河流因暴雨泛滥，1辆汽车被洪水所困，车上3人丧生<ref name="gn67">{{cite web | author = Agencies | date = 2007-06-07 | title = Cyclone Gonu kills 15 | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | work = Gulf News | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906081046/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/cyclone-gonu-kills-15-1.183321 | url = http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/oman/cyclone-gonu-kills-15-1.183321 | archivedate = 2015-09-06}}</ref>。降水引起的洪灾还摧毁了锡斯坦－俾路支斯坦省的一座水坝<ref name="reut610" />。古努在伊朗共导致28人遇难<ref name="imd" />，其中单淹死的就有20人，该国所受破坏估计价值为2兆[[伊朗里亚尔|伊朗里亚尔]]（2007年伊朗里亚尔，相当于同年的2.16亿美元）<ref name="reut610" />。风暴在巴基斯坦[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]到[[瓜达尔|瓜达尔]]之间的阿拉伯海沿岸产生强烈阵风和瓢泼大雨<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120328120400/http://archives.dawn.com/2007/06/06/local16.htm | archivedate = 2012-03-28 | url = http://archives.dawn.com/2007/06/06/local16.htm | title = KARACHI: Light rain in parts of city | publisher = DAWN | date = 2007-06-06 | accessdate = 2012-03-28 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。有报道称，气旋导致瓜达尔东岸近海多艘船只沉没<ref>{{cite web | author = Saleem Shahid | url = http://www.dawn.com/2007/06/06/top15.htm | title = Gwadar boats sink; cyclone nears Oman | publisher = DAWN | date = 2007-06-06 | accessdate = 2010-10-31 | archivedate = 2010-10-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101031062443/http://www.dawn.com/2007/06/06/top15.htm | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。人们还担心前往开放海域的渔船被困。[[俾路支省|俾路支省]]有至少3套房屋和1所学校被毁，210艘泊好的渔船严重受损<ref>{{cite web | author = woeurope.eu | title = Pakistan: Cyclone Gonu | publisher = WeatherOnline | accessdate = 2016-02-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141128190639/http://www.woeurope.eu/cgi-app/reports?ARCHIV=1&LANG=eu&MENU=207&FILE=b1.txt&DAY=20070607&JJA=2007&MMA=06&TTA=08 | archivedate = 2014-11-28 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.woeurope.eu/cgi-app/reports?ARCHIV=1&LANG=eu&MENU=207&FILE=b1.txt&DAY=20070607&JJA=2007&MMA=06&TTA=08}}</ref>。

== 善后和纪录 ==
[[File:Oman_Gonu1.JPG|thumb]]被洪水淹没的街道和翻转的车辆]]
[[马斯喀特国际机场|马斯喀特国际机场]]在古努过去3天后重新开放，富吉拉则在关闭1天后于6月7日重新开放<ref name="Reuters-DialaSaadeh" />。气旋沿途没有对石油设施构成显著影响，虽然油价起初上涨，但之后每桶单价下跌了超过2美元<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 2007-06-08 | title = Oil prices decline by USD2 a barrel after Cyclone Gonu dissipates, easing supply worries | accessdate = 2012-03-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120307221839/http://cyclone-gonu-news.newslib.com/story/10093-160/ | archivedate = 2012-03-07 | url = http://cyclone-gonu-news.newslib.com/story/10093-160/}}</ref>。风暴在北阿拉伯海经过，产生狂风和强烈的[[上升流|上升流]]，这种[[物理海洋学|海洋学]]现象令深海中[[营养素|营养素]]更加丰富的海水上升，取代原本营养素已基本耗尽的海水，促使该海域的[[浮游植物|浮游植物]]出现显著增长<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Wang | first1 = Dongxiao | last2 = Zhao | first2 = Hui | year = 2008 | title = Estimation of Phytoplankton Responses to Hurricane Gonu over the Arabian Sea Based on Ocean Color Data | journal = Sensors | volume = 8 | issue = 8 | page = 4888 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120305224803/https://www.mdpi.org/sensors/papers/s8084878.pdf | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | url = https://www.mdpi.org/sensors/papers/s8084878.pdf | doi = 10.3390/s8084878 | archivedate = 2012-03-05 }}</ref>。此外，古努还令印度洋[[季风|西南季风]]抵达印度[[西高止山脉|西高止山脉]]的时间延迟<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | url = http://www.cybernoon.com/DisplayArticle.asp?section=fromthepress&subsection=inbombay&xfile=June2007_inbombay_standard13145 | date = 2007-06-04 | title = More pre-monsoon showers in city | work = Afternoon Despatch & Courier | accessdate = 2008-05-10 | archivedate = 2008-05-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080510224641/http://www.cybernoon.com/DisplayArticle.asp?section=fromthepress&subsection=inbombay&xfile=June2007_inbombay_standard13145}}</ref>。

风暴导致阿曼的两家海水淡化厂无法正常运作，[[海水淡化|淡水生产]]被迫中断。其中一家是因[[天然气|天然气]]断供导致生产无法继续进行，另一家则是因洪水致使开关设备受损。马斯喀特的63.1万居民及周边地区都需要这两家工厂提供淡水，阿曼东部普遍因此陷入严重缺水境地，官员尝试使用水箱改善局面。5天后，两家工厂恢复运作，供水也基本恢复正常。此外，阿曼各地的停电均由电工迅速恢复。<ref name="ap610">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222214343/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/06/10/cyclone-gonu-causes-water-shortages-in-oman.html | agency = Associated Press | date = 2007-06-10 | title = Cyclone Gonu causes water shortages in Oman | accessdate = 2016-02-16 | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/06/10/cyclone-gonu-causes-water-shortages-in-oman.html | work = Fox News | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>气旋过去5天后，马斯喀特及沿海省份的公共设施已恢复正常，阿曼陆军协助居民返回家园。虽然阿曼政府没有请求国际社会援助，但美国还是通过附近的[[美国海军|海军舰船]]伸出援手，但最终遭拒。<ref name="dn611" />该国在石油出口方面的损失估计有2亿美元<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Reuters | date = 2007-06-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222132923/http://www.arabianbusiness.com/gonu-costs-oman-200m-in-lost-exports-143619.html | url = http://www.arabianbusiness.com/gonu-costs-oman-200m-in-lost-exports-143619.html | title = Gonu costs Oman $200m in lost exports | accessdate = 2016-02-16 | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。古努过后的几个月里，政府拨款清理瓦砾和断裂的树枝树干，同时恢复通往旅游景点的道路通行<ref>{{cite web | author = Government of Oman | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2008-04-10 | archivedate = 2013-11-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131108010421/http://reliefweb.int/report/oman/oman-ministerial-panel-reviews-reconstruction-projects-flood-damaged-areas | title = Ministerial panel reviews reconstruction projects in flood-damaged areas | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/oman/oman-ministerial-panel-reviews-reconstruction-projects-flood-damaged-areas | accessdate = 2016-02-16}}</ref>。此外，阿曼全国民防委员会建起139座临时住宅，安置居民8192人。包括水电在内的各项服务逐渐恢复，居民返回家园。风暴过去两天后，仍然留在避难所的大部分灾民都是来自受灾最严重的地区，其中又以[[古赖亚特|古赖亚特]]最多。<ref>{{cite web | author = Government of Oman | publisher = ReliefWeb | date = 2007-06-17 | title = Oman: Al Ma'amari chairs NCCD meeting | accessdate = 2016-02-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131030094712/http://reliefweb.int/report/oman/oman-al-maamari-chairs-nccd-meeting | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/oman/oman-al-maamari-chairs-nccd-meeting | deadurl = no}}</ref>

[[File:Cyclone_Gonu_(2007)_Meteosat_7_Infrared_Satellite_animation.ogv|thumbnail]]

气旋过后，红十字会伊朗分会及其志愿者一起同军方合作，用卡车和直升机向各村庄运送救援物资。其中锡斯坦－俾路支斯坦省分会向灾民分发了上万张毛毯、1300顶帐篷、400件衣物、8万2000个面包和8万7000支瓶装水。<ref name="irfc611" />共计有6万1558户家庭获得伊朗红十字会援助<ref>{{cite web | author= Iranian Red Crescent Society | date = 2007-06-27 | title = Iran: Distribution of relief & food items among flood stricken people of Sistan Baluchistan | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/iran-islamic-republic/iran-distribution-relief-food-items-among-flood-stricken-people-sistan | publisher = ReliefWeb | accessdate = 2016-02-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131031042221/http://reliefweb.int/report/iran-islamic-republic/iran-distribution-relief-food-items-among-flood-stricken-people-sistan}}</ref>。伊朗政府向灾民提供经济救助，官员参与灾区道路、桥梁和供电系统的修复工作，但部分地点的修理难度较大。风暴过去1周时，仍有多个村庄被洪水包围。<ref>{{cite web|author=International Federation of Red Cross And Red Crescent Societies |date=2007-06-11 |title=Iran: Cyclone Gonu Information Bulletin No. 2 |accessdate=2016-02-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121212233510/http://reliefweb.int/report/iran-islamic-republic/iran-cyclone-gonu-information-bulletin-no-2 |url=http://reliefweb.int/report/iran-islamic-republic/iran-cyclone-gonu-information-bulletin-no-2 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-12-12 }}</ref>

气旋古努创下多项强度纪录。6月3日成为特强气旋风暴时，古努就创下阿拉伯海最强热带气旋的新纪录<ref name="63strongest"/><ref name="Anom">{{cite conference|url=http://ams.confex.com/ams/pdfpapers/137585.pdf |title=Anomalies in meteorological fields over northern Asia and it's [sic] impact on Hurricane Gonu |last=El Rafy |first=Mostafa |publisher=American Meteorological Society |last2=Hafez |first2=Yehia |date=2008-04-23 |conference=28th Conference on Hurricanes and Tropical Meteorology |accessdate=2016-02-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111140810/https://ams.confex.com/ams/pdfpapers/137585.pdf |archivedate=2013-11-11 |format=PDF }}</ref>。之后，风暴风速超过3分钟持续风速每小时220公里的特强气旋风暴强度上限，又成为有纪录以来阿拉伯海首场超级气旋风暴<ref name="imd" />。联合台风警报中心估计古努的最高风力时速为270公里，根据这一数据，风暴同[[1991年孟加拉气旋|1991年孟加拉气旋]]并列成为整个北印度洋的最强热带气旋，即便考虑在其它海域形成后进入该海域的风暴，这一纪录依然保持<ref name="jtwcbt" />。6月6日，古努以风速每小时150公里强度从阿曼最东端[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="imd" />，刷新吹袭阿拉伯半岛热带气旋的最高强度纪录<ref>{{cite web | author = NASA | year = 2007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160112122352/http://www.nasa.gov/vision/earth/lookingatearth/gonu.html | deadurl = no | title = Rare Tropical Cyclone Churns in Arabian Sea | url = http://www.nasa.gov/vision/earth/lookingatearth/gonu.html | accessdate = 2016-02-16 | archivedate = 2016-01-12}}</ref>。这场风暴还以致死50人、经济损失总额42亿美元<ref name="imd" />，创下阿曼历史上最惨重自然灾害的新纪录<ref name="Anom" />。此外，古努还是有纪录以来第2场吹袭伊朗的气旋风暴，距1898年6月4日的第1场已超过99年<ref name="imd" />。

